title: Miley Cyrus & Flaming Lips planning naked concert
text:
CNN Leadership
Miley Cyrus & Flaming Lips planning naked concert Colin Stutz , Billboard Updated 1553 GMT (2253 HKT) October 15, 2015 Miley Cyrus and the Flaming Lips will tour together. Story highlights Lips frontman claims there will be a nude concert The joint tour starts November 19 in Chicago (Billboard) Miley Cyrus and the Flaming Lips are hitting the road next month and -- according to an Instagram post by Lips' frontman Wayne Coyne -- they're planning one show with the performers and audience appearing completely in the nude. Miley Cyrus & her Dead Petz play 'SNL,' announce club tour: Watch The tour supports the two parties' recent collaboratation, Miley Cyrus and Her Dead Petz, starting in Chicago on November 19 and ending December 6 in Boston. Clyne didn't mention with show, if any of these, would be the naked one but he did give a few other details. No Miley? No problem: Watch the Flaming Lips perform 'Dead Petz' tracks According to his post on Thursday, Cyrus is planning a show where the she, the Flaming Lips and the audience are all completely naked and where "white stuff that looks like milk" will be "spewed" everywhere. The concept is for a video, he continued, for the song "Milky Milky Milk." See the post below. Read More A photo posted by Wayne Coyne (@waynecoyne5) on Oct 13, 2015 at 9:14am PDT ©2015 Billboard.
